history.content:
The Undergraduate Social Hours this year will be 4-5pm on the first Wednesday of each month in The Wozniak Lounge.

Please join us to enjoy a snack and socialize with your classmates, faculty, and advisers. These events are open to EECS, L&S CS, CS-intended, and CoE Undeclared students

Dates:

  • 9/7 (after UGrad Research Panel)
  • 10/5
  • 11/2  (subject to change due to conflicting Internship Fair)
  • 12/7 (RRR week event)
  • 2/1
  • 3/1
  • 4/5
  • 5/3 (RRR week event)
